{"tid":475811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習權時代】嚴控對外通訊 Skype在內地下架","createTime":"2017-11-21T12:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T01:52:45.000Z","uid":49391,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"629dcfd6f2e14616e50b253cfaba6b715a9e0091","tid":475811,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:50:00.000Z","msg":"內地進一步嚴控互聯網，特別是民眾與境外的通訊。在過去一個月，內地很多手機應用程式商店都已看不見網路通訊軟體Skype，包括蘋果在中國的APP商店。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》報道有關消息指，內地的使用者抱怨連天，稱從上月底起就無法透過Apple iPhone使用Skype的服務。蘋果發言人指出，已經收到中國公共安全部的通知，有數個網路電話通訊協定不符合當地法規，所以已經在中國商店移除這些APP。<br />\nSkype由微軟擁有，目前仍能在內地使用，但是未來命運難料。<br />\n美國《紐約時報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171121/57487243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57487243&d=2Fy9sHg1tkMoLIOMRMTSnsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7fc554d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57487243&h=b4b0bdb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171121/57487243</a>"},{"pid":"dfae245064c2a6493e42471aa027f2c6dbd15090","tid":475811,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"換言之,即係現存上架的通訊APP都係受緊中共嚴密監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa287800c4281ab413be03272e2ed5c644bf028a","tid":475811,"uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換言之,即係現存上架的通訊APP都係受緊中共嚴密監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係為黨，係為雜種一個，防止有人利用通訊app策劃政變，電話已經可以監聽，係差app"},{"pid":"328e45d83dd83b79a57befcd6a74d41b5a89ebb3","tid":475811,"uid":113187,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換言之,即係現存上架的通訊APP都係受緊中共嚴密監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔駛換言之啦<br />\n<br />\n係大陸download得全部都要俾做足：<br />\n1）自動審查敏感字，咩六四呀 劉曉波呀 要自動刪除 自動report<br />\n2）個資料庫要直連北京，隨時可以查到對話內容<br />\n3) 要有斷路機制，一有突發事件當局可以即刻禁制熄server<br />\n<br />\n做少樣唔好想係大陸上架"},{"pid":"14ba714f93211b3fa82043b0f483f5818fa5de5a","tid":475811,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"支那好快抄一個"},{"pid":"3c4fa5025a92b6b294e9725df9f5f85e3b92b13d","tid":475811,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"德政，最好封鎖全世界，孤立全地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97855c41eebd24fa4b0162701ee510dd9883dcb4","tid":475811,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"吊你老母正常做生意點呀"},{"pid":"cf72560882e878f0e0fdc896dd751d228af42ca8","tid":475811,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"iMessage 同Facetime係咪都監控堆？"},{"pid":"3dcb137157da15c5705b7983109225c9b463d2f7","tid":475811,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吊你老母正常做生意點呀</blockquote><br />\n全宇宙都要用V7"},{"pid":"1381e3f623fbe15e55b90d318b7dc767a5318223","tid":475811,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外資點同國外做生意<br />\n用咩聯繫"},{"pid":"26224436abbe6597f36ab4929c2e1c2efae50f18","tid":475811,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iMessage 同Facetime係咪都監控堆？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蘋果server 都要set 係支那, 你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7a0c2dcbcbfde9acddfc060907c8587075dfbe","tid":4